cost.excludesText:
1. Prices in Canadian dollars do not include the 5% GST (Government Service Tax);

2. Driver and guide service fees (USD$15/CAD$20 per person per day);

3. Meals throughout the trip;

4. Entrance fees for activities mentioned in the itinerary;

5. Other personal expenses, such as laundry, telephone calls, drinks, shopping, pay TV, etc.;

6. Additional costs incurred due to force majeure events such as traffic delays, war, coups, strikes, weather, flight cancellations or schedule changes;

7. Any type of travel insurance.

